Implementation details for pagination:

1. findTaggedVPCs() - Now uses ec2.NewDescribeVpcsPaginator
   - Handles VPCs beyond first 1000 results
   - Error wrapping with fmt.Errorf for better context

2. findTaggedECSClusters() - Now uses ecs.NewListClustersPaginator
   - Collects all cluster ARNs across pages
   - Batch describes clusters (100 per call) to get tags
   - Reduces API calls vs previous single-page approach

3. findTaggedALBs() - Now uses elbv2.NewDescribeLoadBalancersPaginator
   - Collects all ALB ARNs across pages (max 400/page)
   - Uses new batchFetchALBTags() for efficiency

4. batchFetchALBTags() - New helper function
   - Fetches tags for up to 20 ALBs per API call (AWS limit)
   - Returns map[arn]map[tagKey]tagValue
   - Reduces API calls from N to ceil(N/20)

